-create a fsx linking to aws ad or self ad
  -configure ad in windows like dns and installing ad ds and ad lds tools,etc if using aws ad
  -sysdm.cpl->to change domain
  -create users
  -mstsc->to connect using rdp
  -lusrmgr.msc->groups->remote desktop users->add users
  -run command \\(fsx-dns-name)\share->to to open fsx
-to connect to users login into rdp username@domainname.com and password and run above command
-to make users access only particular folders
  -click on folder properties->security->advanced->add only required user
